<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>49</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">见《道藏》第24册第694页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '宋体'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
